      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a distinguished example of automotive engineering, this vehicle has been maintained to an exacting standard, ensuring both mechanical reliability and aesthetic appeal. The interior remains refined and well-appointed, while the powertrain delivers the consistent performance expected of a premium pre-owned selection. This offering represents a sophisticated balance of quality and value for the discerning driver.",
