    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm looking for a new home for my trusty car, and it's honestly been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me, so you can feel confident hitting the road right away! I\u2019ve taken great care of it, and it still has that smooth, comfy feel that makes every trip a breeze. If you're looking for a dependable ride that's ready for its next adventure, this is the one! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to tell you more about it!",
      "price": 33800.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
